I was elected to Congress to get to work for OH-02.

I promised to stand up for my constituents until I was red in the face — must be doing something right! 🇺🇸

@FallonTonight @jimmyfallon https://t.co/erL1dRdrnL

Tax breaks on interest from American-made cars? Love it.

@berniemoreno’s &amp; my USA CAR Act will do just that.

Congress should pass this bill to promote American manufacturing, create American jobs, &amp; keep hard-earned money in taxpayers’ pockets! https://t.co/rpef5DFQdg

My Regulation Decimation Act will codify President Trump’s agenda to slash 10 federal regulations for every new one introduced!

Congress must get to work cutting bureaucratic red tape for American families & businesses.

@RepMarkHarrisNC @RepMichaelRulli @RepStutzman @RepBrandonGill @RepMikeCollins @RepAbraham @RepTonyWied @SenRickScott @SenatorLankford @SenRonJohnson

Are you a high school or college student looking for hands-on experience in STEM?

@NASA continues Ohio’s legacy as a leader in flight &amp; is accepting applications for summer internships. It’s a great way to gain skills for an engaging STEM career!

https://t.co/3NX8dV6PHH

Medal of Honor recipients have earned the highest level of distinction by going over &amp; above the call of duty.

@RepTroyNehls’s Medal of Honor Act will honor our veterans &amp; ensure these heroes get the pension they've earned.

I proudly stand with our service members.

Congress must support law enforcement &amp; border patrol agents as they help fulfill @POTUS’s mandate to make America safe &amp; secure.

@RepCiscomani's Agent Raul Gonzalez Officer Safety Act will hold illegal immigrants accountable &amp; support our officers.

I was proud to support it.

The Corporate Transparency Act puts burdensome requirements on our small businesses.

@ZachNunn’s Protecting Small Business from Excessive Paperwork Act is a good step toward getting rid of this & letting small businesses do what they do best – business!

Yesterday, I proudly supported it.

Last week, I supported the Laken Riley Act to hold illegal aliens accountable for crime.

This week, I’m supporting two more bills to protect women &amp; girls in our country.

@HouseGOP is delivering on our promises.
